# Docker Swarm Course-End Project

## Project Overview
This project demonstrates the deployment of a microservices-based voting application using Docker Swarm.

## Services Deployed
- Vote Service
- Result Service
- Worker Service
- Redis
- PostgreSQL

## Technologies Used
- Docker
- Docker Swarm
- Overlay Networks
- Docker Volumes
- PostgreSQL
- Redis

## Deployment Verification
- Docker Swarm initialized successfully.
- Stack deployed using `docker stack deploy`.
- Services verified using `docker service ls`.
- Containers verified using `docker ps`.
- Application functionality confirmed using local HTTP requests.

## Stack Deployment Command

```bash
docker stack deploy -c myapp.yml myvotingapp
